code: public static DataSet<Edge<Long, Double>> getDefaultEdgeDataSet(ExecutionEnvironment env) {     List<Edge<Long, Double>> edgeList = new LinkedList<>().     for (Object[] edge : DEFAULT_EDGES) {         edgeList.add(new Edge<>((Long) edge[0], (Long) edge[1], (Double) edge[2])).     }     return env.fromCollection(edgeList). }
